View and Edit Your Bot’s Name and Description

When you create a new bot, you give it a name and an optional description that’s not visible to customers. These details can be changed.

To build and manage Einstein Bots: 
Customize Application
OR
Modify Metadata
OR
Manage Bots

In the My Bots list, click  | Edit for your new bot.
In the Bot Information area, click Edit.
Update the name and description for your bot as needed.
